# pipeline:
#   1. FETCH HTML over HTTPS (via reqwest / net/http /
#      Node's http module)
#   2. PARSE HTML into a queryable DOM tree (via
#      scraper / goquery / cheerio)
#   3. QUERY with CSS selectors (jQuery-inspired
#      across all three — the universal selector
#      syntax bridges language boundaries)
#   4. EXTRACT attributes / text / hrefs into language-
#      native data structures
#   5. PROCESS extracted data downstream (verify
#      emails, rank icons, render lessons)
#
